This is the repository for the tomahawk resolvers that are automatically exposed in Tomahawk through KDE's Synchrotron.

Resolvers are manually pushed / upgraded here, and Tomahawk users will be able to install them directly from Tomahawk.

[Binary Resolvers]
Binary resolvers are supported in the binaryresolvers provider. The layout of the directory is as such:

binaryresolvers/
    [name]/
        osx/metadata.desktop
        osx/resolver.zip
        
        windows/metadata.desktop
        windows/resolver.zip
        
    [name]/
        osx/metadata.desktop
        osx/resolver.zip
        
        windows/metadata.desktop
        windows/resolver.zip
